{"tid":969220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮經濟顧問：中國或已盜取蘋果技術","createTime":"2019-01-05T01:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T10:20:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"db119d9d626e41bb7173b21a70284ce093cfb2cf","tid":969220,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T01:07:58.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰持續，兩國仍尋求解決問題之際，美國白宮首席經濟顧問庫德洛（Larry Kudlow）於當地時間周五（4日）表示，蘋果公司的技術可能被中國竊取。庫德洛接受彭博（Bloomberg）訪問時說：「我不想在這裏揣測太多，但蘋果的技術可能已經被中國盜取，現在中國正變得非常有競爭力。」「現在有一些來自中國的迹象表明，他們正在關注這個問題，但我們還不知道，目前還沒有實際（證據）。」<br />\n<br />\n庫德洛發表上述評論前不久，美國貿易代表辦公室早前宣佈，美國和中國官員下星期將在北京舉行會談，討論貿易問題。目前，兩國正處於90天的休戰期，致力於解決這場在全球市場引起動盪的貿易糾紛，缺乏知識產權保護，以及強逼技術轉移，正是美方對中國的主要指摘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190105/59107030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190105%2F59107030&d=T%2BVPokq4AxVzfGzn8bEIOW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=eccf73c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190105%2F59107030&h=10cdc633\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190105/59107030</a>"},{"pid":"60842dfba3e7385fcb62c0e625e52ed5bd4e4644","tid":969220,"uid":51932,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T01:11:04.000Z","msg":"Gay cook送㗎，條奶共仆街"},{"pid":"370312147b060f6ffa36ea582c55a9b47559fce5","tid":969220,"uid":1524,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T01:24:04.000Z","msg":"Apple自己揀"},{"pid":"760f57339b0b9a65331662291374418155edb089","tid":969220,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T01:25:26.000Z","msg":"不想揣測太多...."},{"pid":"a9dc023ff411a9ff8674d375a519e835a1e0e623","tid":969220,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T01:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"